-- Sebastian Vettel Agrees to Extend Red Bull Contract Through 2015
-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 2013-06-11T18:07:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-11/sebastian-vettel-agrees-to-extend-red-bull-contract-through-2015.html
Three-time Formula One world
champion Sebastian Vettel has agreed on a contract extension
with  Red Bull  to the end of 2015, his team said in a statement.  The 25-year-old German driver has won three races this
season, including the Canadian Grand Prix at Montreal last
weekend. He leads the standings by 36 points.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter-Joseph Hegarty at 
 phegarty@bloomberg.net  